title: EastEnders viewers left in hysterics as Dot stumbles across internet porn
text:
EastEnders viewers left in hysterics as Dot stumbles across internet porn 
Dot might want some lessons in refining her searches before she looks up bushes By Lauren Franklin, Showbiz Reporter 23rd February 2017, 7:53 pm DOT Branning is a woman of the 21st century, but that doesn’t mean she free from issues with “the Google”. 
Thursday night’s EastEnders saw the God-fearing great-gran take to the internet to look up bushes – however she was shocked at what she found. BBC/EASTENDERS 2 Dot Cotton was shocked when her “bushes” internet search didn’t bring the desired results 
While cameras didn’t show poor Dot’s X-rated sight, she looked horrified and quickly shut the screen. 
Later on when Abbi asked her how her search was coming along, Dot complained that there was: “Ladies popping up with no bras.” 
Viewers found Dot’s rude welcoming hilarious. BBC/EASTENDERS The great-gran told Abi she was shocked to see women with no bras on 
One wrote: “Omg that @bbceastenders opening was the best ever #OhISay #EastEnders” 
A second tweeted: “Dots face when getting the results after typing ‘bushes’ into a search engine 😂😂😂😂 #eastenders” 
Someone else addred: “Oh Dot, you dirty mare” 
And another gave the soap a huge accolade: “And #Eastenders just gives us the best opening in soap history: Dot Googling ‘Bushes’.” 
One step at a time, Dot.
